 2012-10672012-09-07,  ,  ,  ,  DFAIT
ActState Immunity Act
SubjectOrder Establishing a List of Foreign State Supporters of Terrorism
PrecisOrder establishing a LIST OF FOREIGN STATE SUPPORTERS OF TERRORISM in order to prevent listed states from invoking the defence of state immunity when faced with a suit resulting from a terrorist act that can be demonstrated to be linked to the state.
